      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance. This specimen resides in a state of immaculate preservation, exhibiting a level of care that exceeds standard expectations. From its flawless exterior finish to an interior that remains in showroom condition, every detail reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its original factory delivery state in both aesthetics and mechanical integrity.",
